<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,151,2013]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,266,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">Notes</emphasis>
. In the description, 
<bibRefCitation author="Draudt" box="[491,693,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" refString="Draudt, M. (1950) Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Agrotiden-Fauna Chinas aus den Ausbeuten Dr. H. Hone's. Mitteilungen der Munchner Entomologischen Gesellschaft, 40 (1), 1 - 174." type="journal article" year="1950">
Draudt (
<number box="[584,645,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" value="1950.0">1950</number>
: 
<number box="[656,685,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" value="63.0">63</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
mentions “a few specimens from Tai-pei-shan, 
<date box="[1231,1425,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" value="1936-07-13" valueMax="1936-08-25" valueMin="1936-07-13">
<number box="[1231,1258,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" value="13.0">13</number>
.vii.– 
<number box="[1315,1345,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" value="25.0">25</number>
.viii. 
<number box="[1394,1425,511,536]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" value="36.0">36</number>
</date>
” [translated from 
<collectingCountry box="[338,434,548,572]" name="Germany" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">German</collectingCountry>
], later he labelled a male and a female as 
<typeStatus box="[904,1002,548,573]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">holotype</typeStatus>
and allotype [subsequent, invalid 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,549,573]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">type</typeStatus>
designation], at least the 
<typeStatus box="[445,532,584,608]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">syntype</typeStatus>
dated 
<date box="[615,686,583,608]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">
<number box="[615,644,583,608]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553" value="13.0">13</number>
.vii.
</date>
is missing. The specimen chosen by Draudt as “ 
<typeStatus box="[1263,1372,583,608]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">Holotype</typeStatus>
” was designated as the 
<typeStatus box="[349,452,620,645]" pageId="2" pageNumber="553">lectotype</typeStatus>
here.
</paragraph>
